ğŸ§¾ Best Practices
âœ… Use DTOs for external API models (avoid exposing internal entities directly)
âœ… Use dependency injection for services and repositories
âœ… Add Model validation using [Required], [Range] etc.
âœ… Use Status Codes properly: 200 OK, 201 Created, 204 NoContent, 404 NotFound
âœ… Add logging using ILogger
âœ… Keep controller thin and push logic to services
âœ… Use Global exception middleware for better error handling
âœ… Secure APIs with Authentication & Authorization (later stages)
âœ… Add unit tests using xUnit and Moq (in advanced stage)

ğŸš€ Path to Expertise

Level	Goals
ğŸŸ¢ Beginner	Understand HTTP Verbs, Build basic CRUD, Test using Swagger/Postman
ğŸŸ¡ Intermediate	Use DTOs, Model Validation, Services, Repository Pattern
ğŸ”´ Advanced	Add Authentication (JWT), Use Entity Framework + DB, API Versioning, Serilog Logging, Exception Handling
ğŸŸ£ Expert	Write Unit Tests, Integrate Swagger with XML Comments, Deploy to Azure, Use API Gateway, Microservices
